it wasn't this dude.

00:04:49.955 --> 00:04:53.559
Anyway, so I was able
to talk to him.

00:04:53.559 --> 00:04:55.128
I talked to him,
and I got to a truce,

00:04:55.128 --> 00:04:57.363
