the Jews, the Palestinians.

00:06:09.401 --> 00:06:12.872
They'll all bow before me!"

00:06:12.872 --> 00:06:14.407
The power's already gone
to my head.

00:06:14.407 --> 00:06:15.975
Maybe I should wait.

00:06:15.975 --> 00:06:19.245
